\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"assets/images/home_welfare/icon_10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"176\" height=\"176\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>昼食補助</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<!-- //pg_tabpanel_body --></div>\n\t\t\t\t<!-- //pg_tabpanel_inner --></div>\n\t\t\t<!-- //pg_tabpanel --></section>\n\t\n\t\t\t<section id=\"panel_org\" class=\"pg_tabpanel __org\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"tab_org\" hidden=\"until-found\" data-tabpanel>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pg_tabpanel_inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pg_tabpanel_header\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"pg_tabpanel_title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"en\" lang=\"en\">ORG CHART</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ja\">組織図</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pg_tabpanel_icon __org\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"assets/images/home_org/tabpanel_icon.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"171\" height=\"126\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<!-- //pg_tabpanel_header --></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pg_tabpanel_body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pg_org_table\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!-- button type=\"button\" class=\"pg_icon_zoom\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"assets/images/home_org/icon_zoom.png\" alt=\"拡大\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</button -->\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"pg_org_table_img\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"assets/images/home_org/table_202511.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"493\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<!-- //pg_tabpanel_body --></div>\n\t\t\t\t<!-- //pg_tabpanel_inner --></div>\n\t\t\t<!-- //pg_tabpanel --></section>\n\n\t\t\t<section id=\"panel_question\" class=\"pg_tabpanel __question\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"tab_question\" hidden=\"until-found\" data-tabpanel>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pg_tabpanel_inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pg_tabpanel_header\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"pg_tabpanel_title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"en\" lang=\"en\">QUESTION</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ja\">よくある質問</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pg_tabpanel_icon __question\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"assets/images/home_question/tabpanel_icon.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"191\" height=\"170\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<!-- //pg_tabpanel_header --></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pg_tabpanel_body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<dl class=\"pg_qanda\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pg_qanda_shelf\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<dt class=\"pg_qanda_q\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"pg_icon_q\">Q</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t必要な資格はありますか？\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<dd class=\"pg_qanda_a\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"pg_icon_a\">A.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t通勤や業務のため、普通自動車免許が必要です。\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</dd>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pg_qanda_shelf\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<dt class=\"pg_qanda_q\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"pg_icon_q\">Q</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t転勤はありますか？\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<dd class=\"pg_qanda_a\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"pg_icon_a\">A.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tありません。勤務地は業務によりますが、基本的に水戸ヤクルト販売エリア内でご自宅から通える範囲です。\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</dd>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pg_qanda_shelf\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<dt class=\"pg_qanda_q\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"pg_icon_q\">Q</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t新卒採用の募集人数は何人ですか?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<dd class=\"pg_qanda_a\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"pg_icon_a\">A.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t2~3名を予定をしています。当社の求める人物像に近い方がいらっしゃれば積極的に採用をさせていただきます。\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</dd>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pg_qanda_shelf\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<dt class=\"pg_qanda_q\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"pg_icon_q\">Q</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tお休みはどのくらいありますか？\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<dd class=\"pg_qanda_a\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"pg_icon_a\">A.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t日曜日、祝日、月４日間の公休、ほか会社指定日です。（夏季休暇・年末年始）<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tまた、有休制度が完備されており半日や時間単位での使用も可能です。\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</dd>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</dl>\n\t\t\t\t\t<!-- //pg_tabpanel_body --></div>\n\t\t\t\t<!-- //pg_tabpanel_inner --></div>\n\t\t\t<!-- //pg_tabpanel --></section>\n\n\t\t<!-- //pg_tab_body --></div>\n\t<!-- pg_tab_wrap --></div>\n\n\t<section class=\"pg_numbers\">\n\t\t<h2 class=\"md_title\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"ja\">数字でみる水戸ヤクルト販売</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"en\" lang=\"en\">NUMBERS</span>\n\t\t</h2>\n\t\t<div class=\"pg_numbers_inner\">\n\t\t\t<ul class=\"pg_numbers_lists\">\n\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(min-width:769px)\" srcset=\"assets/images/home_numbers/icon_01_pc.png\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"assets/images/home_numbers/icon_01_sp.png\" alt=\"創業年数 58年\" width=\"140\" height=\"140\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(min-width:769px)\" srcset=\"assets/images/home_numbers/icon_02_pc.png\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"assets/images/home_numbers/icon_02_sp.png\" alt=\"平均有給取得日数 10日\" width=\"140\" height=\"140\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(min-width:769px)\" srcset=\"assets/images/home_numbers/icon_03_pc.png\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"assets/images/home_numbers/icon_03_sp.png\" alt=\"男女比（正社員） 女性53%、男性47％\" width=\"140\" height=\"140\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(min-width:769px)\" srcset=\"assets/images/home_numbers/icon_04_pc.png\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"assets/images/home_numbers/icon_04_sp.png\" alt=\"年間休日 120日（2025年年度）\" width=\"140\" height=\"140\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(min-width:769px)\" srcset=\"assets/images/hom